      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 42 初九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 42 初九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九：利用為大作，元吉，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first NINE, undivided, shows that it will be advantageous for its subject in his position to make a great movement. If it be greatly fortunate, no blame will be imputed to him.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="yijing-042-yi__alignment-003">
      <prop type="x-work-id">yijing</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">yijing-042-yi</prop>
