      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 42 六四</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 42 六四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六四：中行，告公從。利用為依遷國。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth SIX, divided, shows its subject pursuing the due course. His advice to his prince is followed. He can with advantage be relied on in such a movement as that of removing the capital.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
