      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 42 九五</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 42 九五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九五：有孚惠心，勿問元吉。有孚惠我德。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth NINE, undivided, shows its subject with sincere heart seeking to benefit (all below). There need be no question about it; the result will be great good fortune. (All below) will with sincere heart acknowledge his goodness.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
