      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 42 上九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 42 上九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上九：莫益之，或擊之，立心勿恆，凶。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the sixth NINE, undivided, we see one to whose increase none will contribute, while many will seek to assail him. He observes no regular rule in the ordering of his heart. There will be evil.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
